This folder contains Terraform code to provision complete AWS infrastructure required for the microservices e-commerce application.

Infrastructure includes:

VPC
Public & Private Subnets
Internet Gateway & NAT
EKS Cluster
IAM Roles
Security Groups

All resources are created using Terraform modules for reusability and clean code structure.

